	(text_box "FT-01.kicad_sch  (top level - just sheet symbols + net labels)\n│\n├── power.kicad_sch\n│     USB-C connector, CC resistors, TP4056, LiPo pads,\n│     AMS1117, bulk caps, VBAT divider to ADC\n│\n├── mcu.kicad_sch\n│     ESP32-S3 N16R8, decoupling caps, strapping pins,\n│     EN/RST filter, SWD header, all net labels out\n│\n├── display.kicad_sch\n│     SSD1680 FPC connector, W25Q128, SPI net labels,\n│     CS/DC/RST/BUSY routing\n│\n├── sensors.kicad_sch\n│     DS3231 + crystal + backup battery,\n│     MPU6050 module header, VL53L0X module header,\n│     I2C net labels, AD0 pull-up\n│\n├── peripherals.kicad_sch\n│     WS2812B + decoupling cap,\n│     Side LEDs + current resistors,\n│     Buzzer + transistor driver,\n│     Laser + constant current driver\n│\n└── io.kicad_sch\n      Tactile buttons + debounce,\n      USB-C data lines (if using USB),\n      UART/debug header,\n      Any expansion pads"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 14.732 15.24 0)
